Class Vector3f

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.groep6.pfor.util.Vector3f

  • public class Vector3f
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a vector in 3d space. Has mathematical applications mostly used for colors.
    Author:
    Nils van der Velden
